 mt-8 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Our Mission\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Our mission is to bridge the gap between complex government policy and the citizens who need it most. By utilizing advanced AI and aggregating data directly from official public sources (including \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://myscheme.gov.in\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"text-brand-500 underline hover:text-brand-600\",\"children\":\"myscheme.gov.in\"}],\", PIB, and MyGov), we democratize access to welfare information.\"]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-8 mb-4\",\"children\":\"What Makes Us Different\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm rounded-2xl text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl mb-3 block\",\"children\":\"🆓\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\",\"children\":\"100% Free\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Completely free to browse, search, and check eligibility. No hidden fees, ever.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm rounded-2xl text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl mb-3 block\",\"children\":\"🌐\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\",\"children\":\"Multilingual\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Scheme guides available in English, Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Marathi and more regional languages.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"card p-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm rounded-2xl text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl mb-3 block\",\"children\":\"🔄\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-bold text-slate